                        "description": "Confirms a QUOTED transfer. Runs compliance checks:\n- Auto-APPROVED → initiates payout → PAYOUT_PENDING\n- COMPLIANCE_PENDING → awaits manual review\n- COMPLIANCE_REJECTED → blocked country or sanctioned name"
                    },
                    "response": []
